Source: cmonitor
Section: base
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Francesco Montorsi <francesco.montorsi@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>=10), libgtest-dev
Standards-Version: 4.0.0
Homepage: https://github.com/f18m/cmonitor

Package: cmonitor-collector
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: a container performance monitoring solution
 A Docker/LXC, database-free, lightweight container performance monitoring solution, perfect for ephemeral containers
 (e.g. containers used for DevOps automatic testing). Can also be used with InfluxDB and Grafana to monitor long-lived 
 containers in real-time.


Package: cmonitor-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: a container performance monitoring solution
 A Docker/LXC, database-free, lightweight container performance monitoring solution, perfect for ephemeral containers
 (e.g. containers used for DevOps automatic testing). Can also be used with InfluxDB and Grafana to monitor long-lived
 containers in real-time.
